      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-05/country-garden-s-sales-drop-most-in-years-amid-wind-up-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[碧桂园控股公司(Country Garden Holdings Co.)公布了至少七年来最大的销售额跌幅，这加剧了这家中国房地产开发商的困境，该开发商目前正面临寻求清算的诉讼。]]></description>
